<!-- Modal -->
<div id="reportModal" class="modal hide fade">
  <div class="modal-header">
	<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
	<h3 id="myModalLabel">Report a Bug <span class="badge">+50</span></h3> 
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
	<p>If you find a bug in one of our projects, post the issue with a breaking test case to GitHub. We'll flag your post as a bug, award you the points, and attach an award to it for anyone who can fix the bug.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Modal -->
<div id="bugModal" class="modal hide fade">
  <div class="modal-header">
	<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
	<h3 id="myModalLabel">Fix a Bug <span class="badge">+100</span></h3> 
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
	<p>Look for posts with a green point badge next to the title. This indicates that points can be awarded for providing a solution to the issue. Post your solution in the same venue as the original post. If your solution is accepted, you'll earn those points!</p>
  </div>
</div>
